data.description: It is nestled in the peaceful cul-de-sac of the Greystone subdivision in the sought-after city of Perry, GA. A home that would be a fantastic place to raise a family or a quiet place for empty nesters. Features: Beautiful tall doors throughout. Large Kitchen Island. Granite countertops, Large walk-in pantry. Adorable Mudroom. Smart Refrigerator included. LVP Floors. Cover front porch and back patio. Large Laundry Room and Linen Closet with custom shelves, Bonus Room/4th bedroom upstairs with closet and full bath. Walk-in attic with floors for storage and two water heaters. Each floor has a separate HVAC unit. The Master bath features a large walk-in tile shower, garden tub, and double granite vanity. Did I mention the Cul-de-sac? Easy to show. Please schedule at least an hour in advance. The furniture is also for sale.
